resource/Sligo\", \"score\": 0.9998192268554676, \"rank\": 0.00016599562142125785, \"text\": \"Sligo\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sligo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sligo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"McSharry\", \"from\": 167, \"to\": 175}, {\"ngram\": \"her heroic exploits\", \"from\": 204, \"to\": 223}, {\"ngram\": \"Monday\", \"from\": 256, \"to\": 262}, {\"ngram\": \"the bronze\", \"from\": 298, \"to\": 308}, {\"ngram\": \"a packed La Defense Arena\", \"from\": 312, \"to\": 337}, {\"ngram\": \"a time\", \"from\": 343, \"to\": 349}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She will be in lane five of the pool for the first heat in the morning, scheduled to start at 10am, with the woman who took the gold on Monday night, Tatjana Smith, alongside her in lane four.\", \"from\": 363, \"to\": 555, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"lane\", \"from\": 378, \"to\": 382}, {\"ngram\": \"the pool\", \"from\": 391, \"to\": 399}, {\"ngram\": \"the first heat\", \"from\": 404, \"to\": 418}, {\"ngram\": \"the morning\", \"from\": 422, \"to\": 433}, {\"ngram\": \"the woman\", \"from\": 468, \"to\": 477}, {\"ngram\": \"the gold\", \"from\": 487, \"to\": 495}, {\"ngram\": \"Monday night\", \"from\": 499, \"to\": 511}, {\"ngram\": \"Tatjana Smith\", \"from\": 513, \"to\": 526}, {\"ngram\": \"lane\", \"from\": 545, \"to\": 549}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Smith is also the Olympic record holder in this discipline, setting a time of 2:18.95 in Tokyo in 2021.\", \"from\": 557, \"to\": 660, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 646, \"end\": 651, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9999675893022916, \"rank\": 3.241174729448549e-05, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Smith\", \"from\": 557, \"to\": 562}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic record holder\", \"fro